## Course Overview

MAE 4190: Fast Robots is a hands-on course in the Cornell College of Engineering focused on:

- **Embedded Systems**: Microcontroller programming and real-time control
- **Mechatronics**: Electrical integration and sensors
- **Autonomous Control**: Obstacle avoidance and feedback control

